Content-Based Recommendation

Uses TF-IDF Vectorization on news article text to capture semantic meaning.

Computes cosine similarity to recommend articles similar to the user-entered news title.

Collaborative Filtering

Analyzes user interaction data (click behavior).

Builds a user-item interaction matrix and computes similarity using cosine distance.

Recommends articles based on similar usersâ€™ preferences.

Hybrid Recommendation Approach

Combines content-based and collaborative results.

Improves recommendation accuracy and handles sparsity in user data.

Cold-Start Handling

Safely handles new users by providing popular or content-based recommendations.

Web Interface

Simple and intuitive UI for entering User ID and News Title.

Displays recommended articles with category, subcategory, summary, and direct links.
